to say Happy Birthday to you!

20:36.131 --> 20:37.583
Aw. There you are. What's up, man?

20:37.732 --> 20:39.379
How you doing, bro? Hey, thank you, man.

20:39.380 --> 20:40.663
Hey, kip, thanks for coming.

20:40.987 --> 20:42.210
