20:45.148 --> 20:47.055
Your songs are much happier than mine are.

20:47.253 --> 20:49.762
I don't know, bud. You look
pretty happy right there, bud.

20:50.524 --> 20:52.504
Jolene, how you doing? Good to see you.

20:52.505 --> 20:53.577
