23:32.710 --> 23:34.146
Would you be willing to come by and...

23:34.948 --> 23:36.040
I just wanna play you something.

23:36.041 --> 23:37.316
Sure. See you in a bit.

23:38.074 --> 23:39.690
You're a sweetheart. All
right, I'll see you.

23:43.581 --> 23:45.669
