Hmm. So how can I help you?

24:02.219 --> 24:03.945
Could have treated my daughter better.

24:04.705 --> 24:05.598
Huh.

24:06.849 --> 24:10.302
With all due respect, I did that...
for 13 years.

24:10.929 --> 24:12.319
