words from the birthday boy?

27:07.257 --> 27:08.997
Deacon, get your butt up here.

27:09.068 --> 27:10.069
Aw, man.

27:10.070 --> 27:11.347
All right. Okay. Um...

27:14.878 --> 27:15.784
Do I have to?

27:16.237 --> 27:17.451
Come on. You have to admit,

27:17.452 --> 27:18.636
this is more fun than sittin' at home

27:18.637 --> 27:20.233
watchin' a sad movie by yourself.

27:22.589 --> 27:25.467
For the record, "old yeller"
is not a sad movie.

27:25.468 --> 27:28.404
It is the uplifting tale
of the unconditional love

27:28.405 --> 27:29.903
between a boy and his dog.

27:32.388 --> 27:34.050
It's easy to forget how
many friends you have,

27:34.051 --> 27:37.615
and you guys sure do know how
to make a man feel, uh...

27:37.731 --> 27:38.720
Appreciated.

27:38.828 --> 27:40.207
And let's not do this again next year.

