38:47.141 --> 38:49.312
Hey, what am I supposed to do with this?

38:51.061 --> 38:52.846
Love him, I think.

38:57.830 --> 38:58.753
Mr. mayor.

38:59.782 --> 39:02.594
Hey, there he is. Come on in, Cole.

39:03.638 --> 39:04.786
Please have a seat.

39:05.799 --> 39:07.921
I was beginning to think you
were gonna stand me up.

39:08.743 --> 39:10.050
Well, the thought did cross my mind.

39:10.854 --> 39:13.827
I have to say, uh, sorry to hear
about you and Rayna. Thank you.

39:14.213 --> 39:16.274
I hope that's not the reason
you asked me in today.

39:16.279 --> 39:17.850
No, no, no. It's not.

39:18.278 --> 39:19.684
Though in days gone by,

39:19.685 --> 39:21.777
I would've appreciated your
friendship during all this.

39:22.550 --> 39:23.538
Your counsel.

