I doubt she'd have me now.

39:29.734 --> 39:31.584
Oh, she still cares about you, Coleman,

39:32.086 --> 39:32.961
and so do I.

39:33.942 --> 39:36.340
I never imagined how
ugly this would all get,

39:36.341 --> 39:38.770
